name: Senorita_Dido
text:
Senorita Dido
Senorita Dido was a woman who resided in a fortress atop a rocky atoll on the purple sea. 
Biography
Following a 1945 nuclear test, Senorita Dido sat in a room, listening to a phonograph. A mechanism in the room began to emit a strange noise and the Fireman came to investigate before leaving the room.
Senorita Dido followed him to a theater, where he was levitating and emitting a golden cloud, from which an orb containing the image of Laura Palmer appeared. It floated to her hands and she kissed it before sending it to Earth.
